{
  "id": "nce2-l51",
  "title": "Lesson 51: Reward for Virtue",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/51ÔºçReward for Virtue.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Why did Hugh's diet not work?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.28,
      "endTime": 15.32
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "My friend, Hugh, has always been fat,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.33,
      "endTime": 19.76
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "but things got so bad recently that he decided to go on a diet.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 19.77,
      "endTime": 26.31
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "He began his diet a week ago.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 26.32,
      "endTime": 29.6
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "First of all, he wrote out a long list of all the foods which were forbidden.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 29.61,
      "endTime": 36.87
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The list included most of the things Hugh loves:",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.88,
      "endTime": 41.29
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "butter, potatoes, rice, beer, milk, chocolate, and sweets.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.3,
      "endTime": 48.63
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Yesterday I paid him a visit.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 48.64,
      "endTime": 51.96
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I rang the bell and was not surprised to see that Hugh was still as fat as ever.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.97,
      "endTime": 59.27
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He led me into his room and hurriedly hid a large parcel under his desk.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 59.28,
      "endTime": 65.79
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It was obvious that he was very embarrassed.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 65.8,
      "endTime": 70.02
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When I asked him what he was doing,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 70.03,
      "endTime": 72.69
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "he smiled guiltily and then put the parcel on the desk.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.7,
      "endTime": 77.77
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He explained that his diet was so strict that he had to reward himself occasionally.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 77.78,
      "endTime": 85.58
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Then he showed me the contents of the parcel.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 85.59,
      "endTime": 89.34
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It contained five large bars of chocolate and three bags of sweets!",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.35,
      "endTime": 94.35
    }
  ]
}